  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/8aa042832badf36892c17fa23ed48e66.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span>Due to cruel governing policies and corrupt noblemen, a rebellion is beginning to unfold in Hozuki.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Byakuya, the rebel organization that fights the shogunate, has recruited many of the strongest warriors in the land, and all of them have a grudge against the shogunate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The shogunate's elite fighting force, Hozuki, is home to the only ones that can stand against them. Mukuro, Momo, and Kinako must do battle to win true peace for Yamato once and for all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/a0d8464aa6854976e4f39c683b9f1d02.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span>Interrogate the locals to find important hints about the nature of your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight in turn-based battles as you explore all over the country of Yamato!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap between two characters, both of whom have unique abilities in battle, at various points in the story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/09f64c2d6caf1de8f256724e9f281472.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/5f5d1a9d2e34c64d83755e8bdb2f1a9c.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/42ab82de64fa3ec9065dc43ca95755e6.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/9f486a4f799b91b9540e4a43c90adcda.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/0f5bc44fb16ac5e66633f189d10b6756.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/c47c8a5a333fb9f1433bebc1ec3541a2.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>Beautiful Animation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat animations are hand-drawn in an anime style, giving attacks their own flavor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose Your Side</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with the government, join the rebellion, or fight for yourself! The decision is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Fully Expanded Experience</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes all the bonus content introduced after the original release in Japan, with new battles to fight and new relationships to explore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice-Acted Female Cast</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the female characters are voiced, enhancing the emotion of the story!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/8aa042832badf36892c17fa23ed48e66.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span>Due to cruel governing policies and corrupt noblemen, a rebellion is beginning to unfold in Hozuki.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Byakuya, the rebel organization that fights the shogunate, has recruited many of the strongest warriors in the land, and all of them have a grudge against the shogunate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The shogunate's elite fighting force, Hozuki, is home to the only ones that can stand against them. Mukuro, Momo, and Kinako must do battle to win true peace for Yamato once and for all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/a0d8464aa6854976e4f39c683b9f1d02.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span>Interrogate the locals to find important hints about the nature of your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight in turn-based battles as you explore all over the country of Yamato!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap between two characters, both of whom have unique abilities in battle, at various points in the story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/09f64c2d6caf1de8f256724e9f281472.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/5f5d1a9d2e34c64d83755e8bdb2f1a9c.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/42ab82de64fa3ec9065dc43ca95755e6.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/9f486a4f799b91b9540e4a43c90adcda.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/0f5bc44fb16ac5e66633f189d10b6756.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1551670/extras/c47c8a5a333fb9f1433bebc1ec3541a2.avif?t=1749383612\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>Beautiful Animation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat animations are hand-drawn in an anime style, giving attacks their own flavor!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose Your Side</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with the government, join the rebellion, or fight for yourself! The decision is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Fully Expanded Experience</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes all the bonus content introduced after the original release in Japan, with new battles to fight and new relationships to explore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice-Acted Female Cast</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the female characters are voiced, enhancing the emotion of the story!</p>",
